features: SAY GOODBYE TO DIM LIGHTS:We have specially increased the thickness of the cotton wick, and the number of cotton wick strands in each tea lights candles has been increased to 15 strands.With the latest high-quality cotton wicks, our tea lights guarantee you unwavering, beautiful flames. Rest assured, these flames endure without flickering or dimming - a result of rigorous testing that ensures you rarely see any dimming in the flame

4-5 HOUR BURN TIME & NO RESIDUE:Made from premium paraffin wax and reinforced premium cotton wick, this tea lights candles is guaranteed to give you over 4 hours of clean, residue-free burning, making it ideal for events that require a long-lasting, perfect ambience

SMOKELESS&ODORLESS& HEALTH-CONSCIOUS:Breathe Easy with Our Smokeless, Odorless, and Health-Conscious Tea Lights. Our tea lights create a space where you can enjoy the utmost comfort and health, free from any unwelcome odors or smoke, allowing you to fully relax and immerse yourself in a worry-free ambiance

VERSATILE COMPANIONS FOR EVERY OCCASION:Our 300 PACK unscented tea light candles are suitable for a variety of occasions, including parties, weddings, and as decorations for Halloween, Christmas, and Thanksgiving festivities. They can also create a serene atmosphere for meditation and mark special anniversary celebrations.

PACKAGED PERFECTION:Our small tealight candles come in a standard size (1.5 inches wide, 0.6 inches high), thoughtfully packaged in premium boxes. Each candle arrives at your doorstep in impeccable condition, ready to elevate your space and enhance your experience

reviews.reviewText: Got the 200 pack for my mom, of course I had to steal some but package came in very well packaged and great price for quality & quantity.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 8, 2023
Reviewed in the United States on January 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for ambiance or emergencies
reviews.reviewText: I always have candles on hand in case of emergency. I had these for a while before I needed them in a power outage. They are well-made, and the wick is sturdy. They're scentless which is good for my household. The burn time for us was about 3 1/2 hours. In the end, we didn't have to use many of them. 50 lights at this price is a deal, especially with the good burn time of each tea light.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Hours of Tea lights
reviews.reviewText: I am pleased to report that each tealight was intact.. So often, I receive some tea lights that have been crushed, dented, or otherwise damaged.I tested these tea lights in a variety of situations and rooms (because otherwise imperceptible drafts can decrease the life of a tea light. I tried placing them in a safe place by themselves as well as in votives and other tea-light holders. In all cases, these lights performed very well and lasted the stated 4 hours (give or take a few minutes).I have nothing negative to say about these and would happily recommend them to others.Hope this helps!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars some burn for 4-5 and some burn 2-3 all in simular containers
reviews.reviewText: per the Amazon page, I have not received these yet but I did find them on my driveway last night. I tried some last night and they burned for 2 hours. Decided to try again this morning and they burned between 3 to 4 1/2 hours. So not sure they are what they advertise they will do. If you order, watch your shipment, I never received the notice that it was shipping, just found on my driveway.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 23, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars burns all the way through, no residual
reviews.reviewText: burn all the way, and does not leave any residual even if the temperature is cold.easy to use and burn last for over 3 hours. love it for lighting my incense.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 5, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good for many uses
reviews.reviewText: The candles are a little smaller than I expected however they work just fine. I not only use these for ambience but also at my dinner table. They are perfect as a burner to melt butter. They do not have any annoying scent and they last throughout an entire dinner.Two hundred candles will last me a long time and at this price, the value is exceptional.
